1. Compile
--------------
  Enter the following command, 

    make compile

  Then, see the generated file 'foo.s'

2. Assembling
--------------
  Enter the following command, 

    make asm 

  Then, see the generated file 'foo.o'


3. Linking
--------------
  Enter the following command, 

    make link

  Then, see the generated file 'foo'

4. Run SW on CPU
--------------
  Enter the following command

    ./foo

5. Trace CPU with debugger
  Enter the following command

    make gdb

  enter the following sequentially
    break main
    run
    si or ni





